\
\'93I\'92ll love it. I love it now but I just can\'92t think about it. You know\
how I get when I worry.\'94\
\
\'93If I do it you won\'92t ever worry?\'94\
\
\'93I won\'92t worry about that because it\'92s perfectly simple.\'94\
