\'93Then I\'92ll do it. Because I don\'92t care about me.\'94\
\
\'93What do you mean?\'94\
\
\'93I don\'92t care about me.\'94\
\
\'93Well, I care about you.\'94\
\
\'93Oh, yes. But I don\'92t care about me. And I\'92ll do it and then everything\
