\
\'93Doesn\'92t it mean anything to you? We could get along.\'94\
\
\'93Of course it does. But I don\'92t want anybody but you. I don\'92t want any\
one else. And I know it\'92s perfectly simple.\'94\
\
\'93Yes, you know it\'92s perfectly simple.\'94\
\
\'93It\'92s all right for you to say that, but I do know it.\'94\
\
\'93Would you do something for me now?\'94\
\
\'93I\'92d do anything for you.\'94\
\
\'93Would you please please please please please please please stop\
talking?\'94\
\
He did not say anything but looked at the bags against the wall of the\
